00:43:05.802 --> 00:43:08.856
have picked those top
stocks but [INAUDIBLE].

00:43:08.856 --> 00:43:11.660
And with value investing, how
you account for account loss--

00:43:11.660 --> 00:43:14.776
I mean selection bias where
companies have disappeared

00:43:14.776 --> 00:43:16.110
from the data [INAUDIBLE].

00:43:16.110 --> 00:43:18.260
WESLEY GRAY: Yeah
sure, so to the data

00:43:18.260 --> 00:43:20.900
question-- most
researchers enact--

00:43:20.900 --> 00:43:23.960
they use crisp
data, which is they

00:43:23.960 --> 00:43:27.750
have whole teams that try their
best to eliminate this problem.

00:43:27.750 --> 00:43:30.049
Where they get backfill
delisted the data.

00:43:30.049 --> 00:43:32.340
They have someone go hunt
