00:43:32.340 --> 00:43:34.630
was a merger acquisition,
was that because they

00:43:34.630 --> 00:43:36.240
went bankrupt, what have you.

00:43:36.240 --> 00:43:38.970
So that is kind of the gold
standard for doing research

00:43:38.970 --> 00:43:42.210
