00:52:24.460 --> 00:52:26.930
It is so painful to write.

00:52:26.930 --> 00:52:28.970
Like value is kind of painful.

00:52:28.970 --> 00:52:32.180
Momentum you will
die sometimes, right?

00:52:32.180 --> 00:52:34.020
And that's what you want.

00:52:34.020 --> 00:52:37.530
You want strategies
where you've got

00:52:37.530 --> 00:52:41.000
to be the last bag holder
that's willing to be like, no, I

00:52:41.000 --> 00:52:43.200
understand how and
why this works.

00:52:43.200 --> 00:52:46.600
And I want to see it
be horrific sometimes.

00:52:46.600 --> 00:52:48.440
Because now I know
it's sustainable.

00:52:48.440 --> 00:52:49.990
Whereas if I have
a strategy where

00:52:49.990 --> 00:52:51.640
like I do all this
research and it just

00:52:51.640 --> 00:52:54.490
makes money like a
Maddoff return stream,

00:52:54.490 --> 00:52:55.740
I don't want to do that.

00:52:55.740 --> 00:52:57.280
Because there's
tons of physics PhDs

00:52:57.280 --> 00:53:00.020
that are going to figure that
out and arbitrage that away.

00:53:00.020 --> 00:53:04.620
So we want systems that
are mechanically exploiting

00:53:04.620 --> 00:53:09.440
some behavioral issue but also
really painful for basically

00:53:09.440 --> 00:53:11.670
delegated asset managers
to really follow

00:53:11.670 --> 00:53:13.891
in their purest form
because they lose their job.

00:53:13.891 --> 00:53:16.140
But that's good because you
don't have all the capital

00:53:16.140 --> 00:53:17.790
competing in a way.

00:53:17.790 --> 00:53:20.810
And momentum is
totally hair-raising.

00:53:20.810 --> 00:53:24.010
Like, if you're a concentrated
momentum player that's

00:53:24.010 --> 00:53:26.270
trying to exploit
this anomaly, you

00:53:26.270 --> 00:53:29.440
are going to get fired a lot.

00:53:29.440 --> 00:53:30.400
Same thing with value.

00:53:30.400 --> 00:53:33.280
If you're a like a Warren
Buffet-- Warren Buffet

00:53:33.280 --> 00:53:35.610
is unique because he has
kind of captured capital.

00:53:35.610 --> 00:53:40.030
But if you do strategies like
