00:53:47.790 --> 00:53:50.190
That's actually the
greatest signal ever.

00:53:50.190 --> 00:53:53.560
When you see redemptions coming
out on strategies that you know

00:53:53.560 --> 00:53:58.190
work because they exploit
the systematic bias problem.

00:53:58.190 --> 00:53:59.980
Because that's why they work.

00:53:59.980 --> 00:54:03.020
Because the people that
used to believe in them

00:54:03.020 --> 00:54:05.590
and went on the
active side, give up,

00:54:05.590 --> 00:54:07.620
and then they contribute
to the very anomaly

00:54:07.620 --> 00:54:10.290
they're trying to exploit
because they're selling out

00:54:10.290 --> 00:54:11.820
at the worst possible time.

00:54:11.820 --> 00:54:14.840
And you've got to be that weird
person that's the bag holder.

00:54:14.840 --> 00:54:18.370
And that's why active
investing is insanely hard.

00:54:18.370 --> 00:54:20.820
Because you've got
to be a weird person.

00:54:20.820 --> 00:54:24.580
