closet index funds that

00:54:32.480 --> 00:54:34.480
essentially just do what
the Vanguard funds do

00:54:34.480 --> 00:54:35.880
but more expensive.

00:54:35.880 --> 00:54:38.670
You want active
things to be insane.

00:54:38.670 --> 00:54:42.190
Where you just feel painful
sometimes to be in this thing.

00:54:42.190 --> 00:54:43.750
Because then they're
going to work.

00:54:43.750 --> 00:54:45.580
Because they're sustainable.

00:54:45.580 --> 00:54:48.179
And so it's like a
weird dynamic game

00:54:48.179 --> 00:54:49.470
that you have to think through.

00:54:49.470 --> 00:54:51.590
So it's not easy.

