And empirically, we
could investigate

00:57:15.540 --> 00:57:18.230
how and why these anomalies
would get arbitraged away

00:57:18.230 --> 00:57:21.510
because at the exact worst
time when they stop working,

00:57:21.510 --> 00:57:24.070
if you saw tons of
