00:57:28.250 --> 00:57:30.380
But you see the exact opposite.

00:57:30.380 --> 00:57:34.200
Fun flows away from the
short-term losers all the time.

00:57:34.200 --> 00:57:37.607
And that just contributes
to this thing.

00:57:37.607 --> 00:57:39.440
And it also attributes
to why the best poker

00:57:39.440 --> 00:57:40.606
players don't want to do it.

00:57:40.606 --> 00:57:44.656
Because they're losing
